&lt;h2 id=&#34;description&#34;&gt;Description
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;This porject is a text interface that calculate and display statistics (number of transactions,&amp;hellip;) extracted from the Bitcoin&amp;rsquo;s blockchain with Rust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;introduction&#34;&gt;Introduction
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;This project offer the discovery of two univers that&amp;rsquo;s just emerged : Bitcoin&amp;rsquo;s blockchain and Rust. The topic was to manipulate the registers of this cryptocurrencies using a language we didn´t know a thing about. This project was a collaboration with some Polytech&amp;rsquo;s teachers from Montpellier.&lt;/p&gt;
